# Email Classification Tests
# Tests both IMAP and HTTP Submission input paths
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. Start the server with:
#      nohup npx nx dev @ha-bits/cortex --config showcase/email-classification/stack.yaml &
#   2. For IMAP tests, ensure Greenmail is running:
#      docker run -d --name greenmail -p 3025:3025 -p 3110:3110 -p 3143:3143 greenmail/standalone
#   3. Set OPENAI_API_KEY in env vars
#
# Run with httpyac:
#   httpyac showcase/email-classification/email-classification-tests.http --all

@baseUrl = http://localhost:13000

### Health Check
# @name healthCheck
GET {{baseUrl}}/misc/workflows

### Test 1: HTTP Submission - Important Email
# Tests the any-of bit passThrough with an important email via HTTP submission
# @name submitImportantEmail
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/email-classification-test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "submission": {
    "from": "ceo@company.com",
    "subject": "URGENT: Emergency board meeting",
    "body": "All executives must attend the emergency board meeting today at 2 PM. Critical business decisions need to be made."
  }
}

### Test 2: HTTP Submission - Semi-Important Email
# Tests the any-of bit passThrough with a semi-important email
# @name submitSemiImportantEmail
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/email-classification-test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "submission": {
    "from": "manager@company.com",
    "subject": "Project Update - Q1 Roadmap",
    "body": "Hi team, please review the attached Q1 roadmap and provide your feedback by Friday."
  }
}

### Test 3: HTTP Submission - Not Important Email (Newsletter)
# Tests the any-of bit passThrough with a newsletter (should be archived)
# @name submitNotImportantEmail
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/email-classification-test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "submission": {
    "from": "newsletter@techweekly.com",
    "subject": "Your Weekly Tech Digest",
    "body": "Here's what's trending in tech this week: New AI breakthrough announced..."
  }
}

### Test 4: Run workflow without submission (IMAP path)
# Tests fallback to IMAP when no HTTP submission provided
# Requires Greenmail to be running with test emails
# @name runImapPath
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/email-classification-test
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Get Workflow List
# @name getWorkflows
GET {{baseUrl}}/misc/workflows

### Get Specific Workflow Config
# @name getWorkflowConfig
GET {{baseUrl}}/misc/workflow/email-classification-test
